#: ../../remixd.md:8
msgid "Remixd: Access your Local Filesystem"
msgstr ""

#: ../../remixd.md:10
msgid "[![npm version](https://badge.fury.io/js/%40remix-project%2Fremixd.svg)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@remix-project/remixd)"
